=== 构想与编剧 ===
20世纪80年代初，剧作家兼[[环球影业|环球影业]]初级剧本主管[[爱德华·诺麦尔|爱德华·诺麦尔]]满怀抱负，《机器战警》源自他的构想{{refn|group="注"|见以下文献：<ref name="TheDissolveNeumeier">{{cite web | last = Tobias | first = Scott | title = ''RoboCop'' Writer Ed Neumeier Discusses The Film's Origins | archive-date = 2021-04-17 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210417064254/http://thedissolve.com/features/interview/415-robocop-writer-ed-neumeier-discusses-the-films-ori/ | website = The Dissolve | date = 2014-02-13 | access-date = 2022-03-27 | url = http://thedissolve.com/features/interview/415-robocop-writer-ed-neumeier-discusses-the-films-ori/}}</ref><ref name="UproxxRetro">{{cite web | last = Mancini | first = Vince | title = 'RoboCop' At 30 — An Island Of Dark Satire In A Decade Of Cheerleading | url = https://uproxx.com/filmdrunk/robocop-retrospective-30/ | website = Uproxx | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220302051907/https://uproxx.com/filmdrunk/robocop-retrospective-30/ | date = 2017-07-20 | access-date = 2022-03-27 | archive-date = 2022-03-02 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="Goldberg">{{cite magazine | last = Goldberg | first = Lee | date = 1988-02 | title = RoboWriters! | pages = 22–25, 72 | issue = 127 | magazine = Starlog | publisher = Starlog Group, Inc. | access-date = 2022-03-27 | url = https://archive.org/details/starlog_magazine-127/page/n21/mode/2up}}</ref>{{rp|22}}<ref name="SFX">{{cite web | first = Nick | last = Setchfield | title = The Making Of RoboCop – Extended Cut | url = http://www.sfx.co.uk/2012/03/14/the-making-of-robocop-extended-cut/ | website = [[SFX_(杂志)|SFX]] | date = 2012-03-14 | access-date = 2014-10-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141009204117/http://www.sfx.co.uk/2012/03/14/the-making-of-robocop-extended-cut/ | archive-date = 2014-10-09 | dead-url = yes}}</ref>}}。他很喜欢动作片和《[[星際大戰|星際大戰]]》等机器人主题科幻片，对面向成熟观众的漫画书很感兴趣，通过研究寻找有改编潜力的作品<ref name="TheDissolveNeumeier" /><ref name="SFX" /><ref name="Sammon">{{cite magazine | last = Sammon | first = Paul M. | title = Shooting RoboCop | magazine = Cinefex | issue = 32 | date = 1987-11 | url = https://cinefex.com/backissues/issue32.htm | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220304060329/https://cinefex.com/backissues/issue32.htm | access-date = 2022-03-04 | issn = 0198-1056 | archive-date = 2022-03-04 | dead-url = yes}}</ref>{{rp|7}}。1982年科幻片《[[银翼杀手|银翼杀手]]》在[[华纳兄弟|华纳兄弟]]的摄制地点与诺麦尔办公室相邻，他非正式加入剧组了解电影制作<ref name="TheDissolveNeumeier" /><ref name="SFX" /><ref name="Goldberg" />{{rp|22}}，经历为他构思《机器战警》创造条件：“我仿佛从远处想象类似《银翼杀手》的世界，全机械体警察开始感受人类真实情感”<ref name="TheDissolveNeumeier" /><ref name="Goldberg" />{{rp|22}}。诺麦尔用几晚就写出40页大纲<ref name="TheDissolveNeumeier" />。

诺麦尔为环球搜寻素材时看到导演迈克尔·迈纳雄心勃勃的学生视频<ref name="EsquireOral" /><ref name="UproxxRetro" /><ref name="Goldberg" />{{rp|22}}。两人见面探讨各自构想，《机器战警》与迈纳的机器人主题摇滚[[音樂錄影帶|音樂錄影帶]]不无相似。迈纳2014年接受采访时自称曾构思“超级战警”<ref name="EsquireOral" /><ref name="TheDissolveNeumeier" /><ref name="Goldberg" />{{rp|22}}。两人日常工作之余利用夜间和周末通力合作，花两个月讨论构想，再用两到三个月一起写作{{refn|group="注"|见以下文献：<ref name="EsquireOral" /><ref name="TheDissolveNeumeier" /><ref name="Goldberg" />{{rp|22}}<ref name="LATimesNeumeier">{{cite web | last = Mathews | first = Jack | title = The Word Is Out: Good Writing Still Pays Off : Summer Box-office Hits Sparkled On Paper Before They Sparkled On The Screen | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1987-09-01-ca-5462-story.html | website = [[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]] | date = 1987-09-01 | access-date = 2021-04-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210417063855/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1987-09-01-ca-5462-story.html | archive-date = 2021-04-17 | dead-url = no}}</ref>}}。相互缺乏了解导致双方早期合作事倍功半，需要学习如何向对方提出有价值的意见<ref name="Goldberg" />{{rp|22–23}}。

1960年心理恐怖片《[[驚魂記|驚魂記]]》女主角在第一幕遇害，对诺麦尔影响很大，也想早早安排主角丧生。他从漫画书和个人经历的企业文化汲取灵感，意图讽刺20世纪80年代商业文化，例如美国金融业在日本影响日益增长下越来越咄咄逼人，探讨如何提高杀戮效率的17世纪著作《[[五輪書|五輪書]]》在[[华尔街|华尔街]]热卖。他认为底特律汽车工业衰落的主要原因是官僚作风猖獗。诺麦尔在办公室上班时幻想机器闯入会场杀死所有人，片中209机器人在董事会故障杀人的情节由此而来。<ref name="TheDissolveNeumeier" /><ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|7}}<ref name="ViceNeumeier">{{cite web | url = https://www.vice.com/en/article/exa5an/technology-issue-extra-how-not-to-afford-a-flying-car | title = Technology Issue Extra – How Not to Afford a Flying Car | date = 2009-11-05 | website = [[Vice_(雜誌)|Vice]] | access-date = 2022-03-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210424081013/https://www.vice.com/en/article/exa5an/technology-issue-extra-how-not-to-afford-a-flying-car | archive-date = 2021-04-24 | dead-url = no}}</ref>迈纳认为[[罗纳德·里根|罗纳德·里根]]执政时期堪称见利忘义的时代，[[米爾頓·佛利民|米爾頓·佛利民]]与[[芝加哥男孩|芝加哥男孩]]等经济学家在总统和[[中央情报局|中央情报局]]支持下洗劫全球，《机器战警》的作用就是令人轻松一笑。“警察为坚称‘拥有你们’的企业工作同时不忘初心，这就是本片核心。”片中媒体报道时段源自诺麦尔与迈纳的理念，两人1984年12月完成[[待售劇本|待售劇本]]。<ref name="EsquireOral" />

=== 前期发展 ===
[[File:Paul_Verhoeven_Cannes_2016.jpg|thumb]]（2016年）两次拒绝执导本片，直到认同“人物失去身份”的潜在剧情才改变主意]]

剧本初稿题为《机器战警：未来执法》，1985年初交业界友人和同僚审核{{refn|group="注"|见以下文献：<ref name="TheDissolveNeumeier" /><ref name="SFX" /><ref name="LATimesNeumeier" /><ref name="Goldberg" />{{rp|23–24}}}}。一个月后诺麦尔和迈纳接到两份邀约，一份是[[大西洋娱乐集团|大西洋娱乐集团]]<ref name="LATimesNeumeier" />，另一份是导演[[乔纳森·卡普兰|乔纳森·卡普兰]]与制片人乔恩·戴维森代表的猎户座影业<ref name="UproxxRetro" /><ref name="Goldberg" />{{rp|23–24}}。戴维森对[[剝削電影|剝削電影]]和[[B級片|B級片]]制作很有经验，曾参与1980年喜剧片《[[空前绝后满天飞|空前绝后满天飞]]》制作，自称受剧本中的讽刺吸引<ref name="TheDissolveNeumeier" /><ref name="UproxxRetro" /><ref name="Goldberg" />{{rp|23–24}}。他邀请诺麦尔和迈纳观看《[[铁血双探|铁血双探]]》（1968年）、《[[緊急追捕令|緊急追捕令]]》（1971年）、《[[疯狂的麦克斯2|疯狂的麦克斯2]]》（1981年）等电影，表达他希望《机器战警》传达的基调。猎户座影业为项目开[[綠燈_(電影製作)|绿灯]]后，两位编剧开始创作第二稿。<ref name="Goldberg" />{{rp|25}}

戴维森通过旗下托伯影业制作本片<ref name="Niderost">{{cite magazine | last = Niderost | first = Eric | date = 1987-04 | title = On The Beat With "Robocop" | pages = 58–61 | issue = 117 | magazine = Starlog | publisher = Starlog Group, Inc. | url = https://archive.org/details/starlog_magazine-117/page/n57/mode/2up | access-date = 2022-03-28}}</ref>{{rp|58}}<ref>{{cite magazine | last = Drake | first = C.V. | date = 1987-12 | title = Producer Jon Davison | page = 20 | issue = 1 | volume = 18 | magazine = Cinefantastique | publisher = Fourth Castle Micromedia | location = Forest Park, Illinois | url = https://archive.org/details/cinefantastique_1970-2002/Cinefantastique%20Vol%2018%20No%201%20%28Dec%201987%29/page/n19/mode/2up | access-date = 2022-03-28}}</ref>，向两位编剧支付数千美元买断版权，再付2.5万美元改写费。电影一旦上映，两人还能从制片商利润分成八个百分点。<ref name="LATimesNeumeier" /><ref name="DeadlineBlomkamp">{{cite web | first = Mike Jr. | last = Fleming | title =  Neill Blomkamp To Direct New 'RoboCop' For MGM; Justin Rhodes Rewriting Sequel Script By Creators Ed Neumeier & Michael Miner | url = https://deadline.com/2018/07/robocop-neill-blomkamp-directing-robocop-returns-justin-rhodes-ed-neumeier-michael-miner-mgm-1202424639/ | website = Deadline Hollywood | date = 2018-07-11 | access-date = 2022-03-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220302195146/https://deadline.com/2018/07/robocop-neill-blomkamp-directing-robocop-returns-justin-rhodes-ed-neumeier-michael-miner-mgm-1202424639/ | archive-date = 2022-03-02 | dead-url = no}}</ref>范霍文还从未与木偶师、动画师、实景特效设计师合作，戴维森的联络对导演帮助很大<ref name="UproxxRetro" />。制片人提出不以底特律为背景，诺麦尔认为该市衰败的汽车工业对影片很重要，拒绝变更。经猎户座影业提议，克拉伦斯·博迪克与迪克·琼斯狼狈为奸。<ref name="TheDissolveNeumeier" />

卡普兰为执导《[[X计划_(1987年电影)|X计划]]》（1987年）退-{}-出项目，新导演人选直到半年后才敲定，许多人听到片名就表示没兴趣{{refn|group="注"|见以下文献：<ref name="TheDissolveNeumeier" /><ref name="Goldberg" />{{rp|25}}<ref name="IndieWireCast">{{cite web | last = Lyttleton | first = Oliver | title = 5 Things You Might Not Know About Paul Verhoeven's ''RoboCop'',' Released 25 Years Ago Today | dead-url = no | url = https://www.indiewire.com/2012/07/5-things-you-might-not-know-about-paul-verhoevens-robocop-released-25-years-ago-today-108328/ | website = [[IndieWire|IndieWire]] | date = 2012-07-17 | access-date = 2022-03-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220310174212/https://www.indiewire.com/2012/07/5-things-you-might-not-know-about-paul-verhoevens-robocop-released-25-years-ago-today-108328/ | archive-date = 2022-03-10}}</ref><ref name="Warren">{{cite magazine | last = Warren | first = Bill | date = 1987-10 | title = RoboCop The Strong Arm Of The Law | pages = 17–20, 72 | issue = 123 | magazine = Starlog | publisher = Starlog Group, Inc. | url = https://archive.org/details/starlog_magazine-123/page/n15/mode/2up | access-date = 2022-03-28}}</ref>{{rp|19}}<ref>{{cite web | last = Robey| first = Tim | title = RoboCop: The Bloody Birth Of The Original Film | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/10619036/RoboCop-the-bloody-birth-of-the-original-film.html | website = The Dissolve | date = 2014-02-07 | access-date = 2022-03-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220306004408/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/10619036/RoboCop-the-bloody-birth-of-the-original-film.html | archive-date = 2022-03-06 | dead-url = no}}</ref>}}。制片商邀请[[大衛·柯能堡|大衛·柯能堡]]、[[亚力克斯·考克斯|亚力克斯·考克斯]]、[[蒙特·赫尔曼|蒙特·赫尔曼]]执导，赫尔曼后来担任[[第二摄制组|第二摄制组]]导演<ref name="LATimesNeumeier" /><ref name="IndieWireCast" /><ref>{{cite web | last = Rabin | first = Nathan | url = https://www.avclub.com/alex-cox-1798208136 | title = Alex Cox | website = [[影音俱樂部|The A.V. Club]]| date = 2000-09-20 | access-date = 2022-03-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220309195732/https://www.avclub.com/alex-cox-1798208136 | archive-date = 2022-03-09 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。迈纳想当导演，但猎户座影业无意把七百万美元的项目交给新手<ref name="TheDissolveNeumeier" /><ref name="Goldberg" />{{rp|23, 25}}。

迈纳获邀执导《[[绝命武器|绝命武器]]》（1989年），谢绝出任本片第二摄制组导演的机会<ref name="TheDissolveNeumeier" /><ref name="Goldberg" />{{rp|25}}。猎户座影业高管芭芭拉·博伊尔推荐凭《[[青葱岁月_(电影)|青葱岁月]]》赢得认可、刚执导首部英语片《[[冷血奇兵|冷血奇兵]]》的保罗·范霍文<ref name="TheDissolveNeumeier" /><ref name="UproxxRetro" /><ref name="Goldberg" />{{rp|25}}，但他看到剧本第一页就谢绝邀请，令项目进一步延迟<ref name="EsquireOral" /><ref name="UproxxRetro" /><ref name="Goldberg" />{{rp|25}}。博伊尔又给范霍文发去剧本，建议他留意深层含义<ref name="TheDissolveNeumeier" />，后者不为所动，夫人玛蒂娜看过后建议他试试，不要错过类似“人物失去身份”的剧情“灵魂”。范霍文英语还不流利，自承不理解剧本中的讽刺。<ref name="EsquireOral" />看到机器战警返回墨菲故居催生回忆的情节后他终于决定接手<ref name="DallasHistory" /><ref name="EsquireOral" />。

戴维森、诺麦尔、范霍文在[[卡尔弗制片厂|卡尔弗制片厂]]庄园讨论项目<ref name="TheDissolveNeumeier" />。范霍文准备拍成正剧；诺麦尔请导演翻阅包含[[判官爵德|判官爵德]]的《[[公元两千年_(杂志)|公元两千年]]》等漫画书目，以便范霍文理解编剧设想的电影基调<ref name="TheDissolveNeumeier" /><ref name="Goldberg" />{{rp|25}}。诺麦尔与迈纳根据导演要求创作第三版剧本，为赶进度持续工作至深夜甚至带伤作业，新剧本共92页，包含墨菲与刘易斯相恋的子线剧情<ref name="VultureTidbits" /><ref name="TheDissolveNeumeier" /><ref name="Goldberg" />{{rp|25}}。范霍文看过后承认设想有误，决定采用第二版并借鉴漫画书目风格<ref name="TheDissolveNeumeier" /><ref name="Niderost2">{{cite magazine | last = Niderost | first = Eric | date = 1987-09 | title = War, Remembrance and RoboCop | pages = 36, 38 | issue = 122 | magazine = Starlog | publisher = Starlog Group, Inc. | url = https://archive.org/details/starlog_magazine-122/page/n35/mode/2up | access-date = 2022-03-28}}</ref><ref name="Goldberg" />{{rp|25}}。

=== 选角 ===
[[File:Dan_O'Herlihy_1955.JPG|thumb]]

男主角人选用六到八个月才敲定<ref name="UproxxRetro" /><ref name="Warren" />{{rp|19}}，剧组曾考虑[[阿诺·施瓦辛格|阿诺·施瓦辛格]]<ref name="UproxxRetro" />、[[迈克尔·艾恩塞德|迈克尔·艾恩塞德]]<ref name="EmpireIronside">{{cite web | last = De Semlyen | first = Phil | title = '80s Heroes: Michael Ironside | date = 2016-05-16 | access-date = 2022-03-28 | website = [[帝國雜誌|Empire]] | url = https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/80s-heroes-michael-ironside/ | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220309180436/https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/80s-heroes-michael-ironside/ | archive-date = 2022-03-09 | dead-url = no}}</ref>、[[魯格·豪爾|魯格·豪爾]]、[[湯姆·貝林傑|湯姆·貝林傑]]、[[阿曼德·阿山特|阿曼德·阿山特]]<ref name="IndieWireCast" />、[[凯斯·卡拉定|凯斯·卡拉定]]、[[詹姆士·雷瑪|詹姆士·雷瑪]]<ref name="Goldberg" />{{rp|25}}。猎户座影业不久前的《[[终结者|终结者]]》大卖，希望请施瓦辛格出演<ref name="IndieWireCast" />，但他和另外几位人选体型太强壮，穿上机器战警服饰会显得不可信，例如施瓦辛格可能会像[[必比登|必比登]]或[[面团宝宝|面团宝宝]]<ref name="UproxxRetro" /><ref name="EmpireIronside" /><ref name="Warren" />{{rp|19}}。男主角面部在片中绝大多数时间被头盔掩盖，部分演员难以接受。据戴维森透露，当时只有威勒一心愿意出演。<ref name="Warren" />{{rp|19}}他最大的优势在于片酬要求不高，体型因跑马拉松及武术训练控制得很好，而且凭《[[反暴戰士盟|反暴戰士盟]]》成名后他的影迷大都喜欢科幻片。范霍文自称选中威勒主要是因为对方的下巴很适合本片。<ref name="IndieWireCast" /><ref name="Warren" />{{rp|19}}<ref name="Goldberg" />{{rp|23, 25}}威勒与哑剧演员莫尼·亚基姆合作数月，用美式足球制服模拟机器战警装束，达到流畅但收尾时不无僵硬的动作风格<ref name="EsquireOral" /><ref name="IGNHistory">{{cite web | last = Hawker | first = Tim | title = The History Of RoboCop | url = https://www.ign.com/articles/2014/02/06/the-history-of-robocop | website = IGN | date = 2014-02-06 | access-date = 2022-03-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210417060840/https://www.ign.com/articles/2014/02/06/the-history-of-robocop | archive-date = 2021-04-17 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。威勒自称推掉出演《[[金刚复活|金刚复活]]》（1986年）的机会接演本片主要是想与范霍文合作<ref name="SFX" /><ref name="EWWeller30th">{{cite web | url = https://ew.com/movies/2017/09/05/robocop-peter-weller-30th-anniversary/ | title = Peter Weller Explains How He 'Bullsh--ted' His Way Into ''RoboCop'' | website = [[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]]| date = 2017-09-05 | access-date = 2022-03-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220302000903/https://ew.com/movies/2017/09/05/robocop-peter-weller-30th-anniversary/ | archive-date = 2022-03-02 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

[[斯蒂芬尼·齐姆巴丽斯特|斯蒂芬尼·齐姆巴丽斯特]]本已敲定出演安妮·刘易斯，但她出演的电视剧《[[斯蒂尔传奇|斯蒂尔传奇]]》1986年停播后又因人气高涨续拍，不得不因合同义务退-{}-出本片{{refn|group="注"|见以下文献：<ref name="VultureTidbits" /><ref>{{cite web | first = Jay | last = Bobbin | title = ''Remington Steele'' Back For Round 2 | url = https://www.orlandosentinel.com/news/os-xpm-1987-01-01-0100000080-story.html | website = Orlando Sentinel | date = 1987-01-01 | access-date = 2022-03-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220302195146/https://www.orlandosentinel.com/news/os-xpm-1987-01-01-0100000080-story.html | archive-date = 2022-03-02 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Ed | last = Bark | title = Brosnan A Series Star Caught In TV's Trap | url = https://www.sun-sentinel.com/news/fl-xpm-1986-08-12-8602170692-story.html | website = Sun-Sentinel | date = 1986-08-12 | access-date = 2022-03-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220310133423/https://www.sun-sentinel.com/news/fl-xpm-1986-08-12-8602170692-story.html | archive-date = 2022-03-10 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Alexandra | last = Jacobs | title = Actress Roles Over 40? 'It's A Big Fat Zero' | website = [[纽约观察家报|The New York Observer]] | date = 2003-11-24 | url = https://observer.com/2003/11/actress-roles-over-40-its-a-big-fat-zero/ | access-date = 2022-03-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220303113640/https://observer.com/2003/11/actress-roles-over-40-its-a-big-fat-zero/ | archive-date = 2022-03-03 | dead-url = no}}</ref>}}。替代人选南茜·艾伦认为片名《机器战警》实在乏味，但剧本引人入胜。艾伦以金色长发闻名，范霍文不希望人物变成性感花瓶，要求剪短，艾伦为此理发八次才达到导演要求。为演好女警，艾伦请当副警监的父亲提供演出建议，还到警察学院训练。<ref name="SyFyAllen">{{cite web | last = Spry | first = Jeff | title = Exclusive: ''RoboCop's'' Nancy Allen On The Original's Epic Cast Chemistry, The Remake, And Verhoeven Vs. Kershner | url = https://www.syfy.com/syfywire/exclusive-robocops-nancy-allen-originals-epic-cast-chemistry-new-reboot-and-verhoeven-vs | website = Syfy | date = 2014-02-14 | access-date = 2021-07-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210707082121/https://www.syfy.com/syfywire/exclusive-robocops-nancy-allen-originals-epic-cast-chemistry-new-reboot-and-verhoeven-vs | archive-date = 2021-07-07 | dead-url = yes}}</ref>范霍文鼓励艾伦增重并朝更具男子气概的方向演出，她戒烟后就实现增重目标<ref name="VultureTidbits" />。

柯特伍德·史密斯试镜迪克·琼斯和博迪克，此前他主要以电视演出闻名，没演过热卖电影，把本片视为有潜力的B级片<ref name="EsquireOral" />。剧本要求博迪克戴眼镜，类似[[纳粹党|纳粹]]高官[[海因里希·希姆莱|海因里希·希姆莱]]。史密斯对此一无所知，把人物塑造成只会“嘲讽、傻笑的毒枭”，却又故意装成充满智慧的军国分子头目。<ref name="EsquireOral" />艾恩塞德已经演过《[[反攻美国|反攻美国]]》（1987年），不想再演“精神变态”而且无意参与以特效为主要卖点的电影，谢绝出演博迪克的机会<ref name="IndieWireCast" /><ref name="EmpireIronside" /><ref>{{cite web | first = Don | last = Kaye | title = How Total Recall Brought a Memorable Villain to Life | url = https://www.denofgeek.com/movies/how-total-recall-brought-a-memorable-villain-to-life/ | website = Den of Geek | date = 2020-12-07 | access-date = 2022-03-28 | archive-date = 2022-03-12 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220312032812/https://www.denofgeek.com/movies/how-total-recall-brought-a-memorable-villain-to-life/}}</ref>。此外[[罗伯特·皮卡多|罗伯特·皮卡多]]也曾试镜博迪克<ref>{{cite web | first = Adam | last = Pockross | title = Total Recall At 30: Cohaagen, Benny & Johnny Cab Recall Paul Verhoeven's Mind-Bending Masterpiece | url = https://www.syfy.com/syfy-wire/total-recall-at-30-cohaagen-benny-johnny-cab-interviews | website = [[Syfy|Syfy Wire]] | date =  2020-06-01 | access-date = 2022-03-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211110172521/https://www.syfy.com/syfy-wire/total-recall-at-30-cohaagen-benny-johnny-cab-interviews | archive-date = 2021-11-10 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

罗尼·考克斯以往戏路基本局限在好好先生，觉得这导致他难以获得出演更具男子气概人物的机会<ref name="LATimesRonnyCox">{{cite web | last = Mills | first = Nancy | title = Recognizing The Assets Of Recognition | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1987-08-18-ca-2277-story.html | website = Los Angeles Times | date = 1987-08-18 | access-date = 2022-03-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220309195732/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1987-08-18-ca-2277-story.html | archive-date = 2022-03-09 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。范霍文于是请他扮演大反派迪克·琼斯<ref>{{cite web | last = Pockross| first = Adam| title = Ronny Cox Only Played 'Boy Scout Nice-Guys' Until Paul Verhoeven Turned Him Bad | url = https://www.syfy.com/syfywire/ronny-cox-total-recall-interview-cohaagen | website = Syfy | date = June 24, 2020 | access-date = January 18, 2020 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201004215813/https://www.syfy.com/syfywire/ronny-cox-total-recall-interview-cohaagen | archive-date = October 4, 2020 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。考克斯自称演反派“比演好人大约有意思亿万倍”<ref name="AVClubCox">{{cite web | last = Harris | first = Will | url = https://www.avclub.com/deliverance-s-ronny-cox-on-robocop-total-recall-and-t-1798232091 | title = Deliverance's Ronny Cox On ''Robocop'', ''Total Recall'', And The Glory Of ''Cop Rock'' | website = The A.V. Club | date = 2012-07-05 | access-date = 2022-03-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191120104913/https://film.avclub.com/deliverance-s-ronny-cox-on-robocop-total-recall-and-t-1798232091 | archive-date = 2019-11-20 | dead-url = no}}</ref>，琼斯完全没有同情心，是不折不扣的恶魔<ref name="LATimesRonnyCox" />。米盖尔·弗尔对影片前景不是很有信心，但此时急于找工作，什么活儿都愿意接<ref name="SFX" />。老大哥是以[[MCA公司|MCA公司]]高管[[刘·瓦瑟曼|刘·瓦瑟曼]]为原型，诺麦尔觉得此人形象强大甚至令人生畏<ref name="TheDissolveNeumeier" />。电视节目主持人比克斯比·斯奈德是在英国笑匠[[班尼·希爾|班尼·希爾]]基础上美国化而成，而且表现更极端<ref name="EsquireOral" />。电台名流[[霍华德·斯特恩|霍华德·斯特恩]]获邀参加演出，角色未定，但他感觉影片题材很愚蠢而谢绝邀请，电影上映后他颇为赞赏<ref>{{cite web | first = Bradford | last = Evans | title = The Lost Roles Of Howard Stern | url = https://www.vulture.com/2012/02/the-lost-roles-of-howard-stern.html | website = Vulture | date = 2017-02-09 | access-date = 2022-03-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211115153446/https://www.vulture.com/2012/02/the-lost-roles-of-howard-stern.html | archive-date = 2021-11-15 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

=== 摄制 ===
[[File:Ayuntamiento_de_Dallas.jpg|thumb]]摄制，辅以接景技术令建筑显得更高]]

《机器战警》1986年8月6日开始[[主体拍摄|主体拍摄]]，预算1100万美元<ref name="afi">{{cite web | url = https://catalog.afi.com/Catalog/MovieDetails/67061 | title = RoboCop (1987) | publisher = AFI Catalog of Feature Films | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220302195147/https://catalog.afi.com/Catalog/moviedetails/67061 | archive-date = 2022-03-02 | access-date = 2022-03-28 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="DallasObserverVerhoeven">{{cite web | last = Gallagher | first = Danny | url = https://www.dallasobserver.com/arts/paul-verhoeven-tells-us-why-he-picked-dallas-for-robocop-9647557 | title = Director Paul Verhoeven On ''RoboCop'', The Bit Of 'American Nonsense' That Changed His Career | website = Dallas Observer | date = 2017-07-11 | access-date = 2022-03-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220310125706/https://www.dallasobserver.com/arts/paul-verhoeven-tells-us-why-he-picked-dallas-for-robocop-9647557 | archive-date = 2022-03-10 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。[[攝影指導|攝影指導]][[约斯特·瓦卡诺|约斯特·瓦卡诺]]曾与范霍文合拍《青葱岁月》<ref name="DallasObserverVerhoeven" /><ref name="Niderost" />{{rp|58}}。导演本想聘请《银翼杀手》美术总监[[劳伦斯·波尔|劳伦斯·波尔]]，但戴维森提醒他预算有限，花大价钱请设计师就不得不削减机器战警服饰开支<ref name="SyFyAllen" /><ref name="TheDissolveNeumeier" />，最后改请威廉·桑德尔<ref>{{cite news | first = Walter | last = Goodman | title = Film: RoboCop,' Police Drama With Peter Weller | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1987/07/17/movies/film-robocop-police-drama-with-peter-weller.html | newspaper = The New York Times | date = 1987-07-17 | access-date = 2022-03-28 | page = C10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220311023238/https://www.nytimes.com/1987/07/17/movies/film-robocop-police-drama-with-peter-weller.html | archive-date = 2022-03-11 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。赫尔曼执掌第二摄制组，导演部分动作戏<ref>{{cite web | last = Phillips | first = Keith | url = https://www.avclub.com/monte-hellman-1798208062 | title = Monte Hellman | website = The A.V. Club | date = 1999-11-10 | access-date = 2022-03-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220204013632/https://www.avclub.com/monte-hellman-1798208062 | archive-date = 2022-02-04 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

电影基本上全部在[[達拉斯|達拉斯]]取景<ref name="EsquireOral" /><ref name="DallasObserverVerhoeven" /><ref name="DallasNewsLocations">{{cite web | last = Wilonsky | first = Robert | archive-date = 2022-03-02 | url = https://www.dallasnews.com/opinion/commentary/2017/09/08/robocop-now-30-is-still-the-most-dallas-movie-ever-made-despite-being-set-in-detroit/ | title = 'Robocop',' Now 30, Is Still The Most Dallas Movie Ever Made, Despite Being Set In Detroit | website = The Dallas Morning News | date = 2017-09-08 | access-date = 2022-03-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220302195146/https://www.dallasnews.com/opinion/commentary/2017/09/08/robocop-now-30-is-still-the-most-dallas-movie-ever-made-despite-being-set-in-detroit/ | dead-url = no}}</ref>，少量镜头在[[歐文_(德克薩斯州)|欧文]][[拉斯科琳娜_(德克萨斯州)|拉斯科琳娜]]或[[匹兹堡|匹兹堡]]摄制<ref name="THRPage" /><ref name="DallasObserverVerhoeven" /><ref name="LAtimesDesign">{{cite web | last = Viladas | first = Pilar | title = Design In The Movies : Good Guys Don't Live In White Boxes : In Today's Movies, Modern Design Signifies Ambition, Money, Power--and Now Evil. | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1987-11-01-tm-17886-story.html | website = Los Angeles Times | date = 1987-11-01 | access-date = 2021-04-17 | archive-date = 2021-04-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210417070237/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1987-11-01-tm-17886-story.html | dead-url = no}}</ref>。范霍文希望拍摄地点比较现代化，符合“不久的未来”背景<ref name="DallasObserverVerhoeven" />。底特律许多建筑太过低矮或毫无特色，视觉上也不吸引人<ref name="DallasObserverVerhoeven" /><ref name="Warren" />{{rp|19}}。另据诺麦尔透露，底特律[[工会|工会]]影响很大，无疑会抬高摄制成本<ref name="Bates">{{cite magazine | last = Bates | first = Dan | date = 1987-12 | title = On Location With The Cast & Crew of RoboCop | pages = 16–25 | issue=1| volume=18 |magazine = Cinefantastique | publisher = Fourth Castle Micromedia | location = Forest Park, Illinois | url = https://archive.org/details/cinefantastique_1970-2002/Cinefantastique%20Vol%2018%20No%201%20%28Dec%201987%29/page/n15/mode/2up | access-date = 2022-03-28}}</ref>{{rp|17}}，最后只有片头的录像画面短暂出现真正的底特律<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|7}}。芝加哥因美学因素落选，纽约成本太高，另据戴维森透露，猎户座影业希望电影摄制地点远离该司总部，故不考虑加利福尼亚州<ref name="DallasObserverVerhoeven" /><ref name="Warren" />{{rp|19}}。达拉斯和[[休斯敦|休斯敦]]都有许多现代建筑，最后还有局部地区时代更久远、看起来不那么亮丽的达拉斯入选，减少剧组使用炸药的阻力<ref name="DallasObserverVerhoeven" />。影片计划在达拉斯拍九周，但开拍后很快就确知需要延长。制片商看到已拍素材后同意延期并将预算提至1310万美元。<ref name="IGNHistory" /><ref name="afi" /><ref name="LATimesVerhnMakesGood">{{cite web | last = McKenna | first = Christine | title = Verhoeven Makes Good With Violence | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1987-07-18-ca-660-story.html | website = Los Angeles Times | date = 1987-07-18 | access-date = 2022-03-28 | archive-date = 2022-03-10 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220310125701/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1987-07-18-ca-660-story.html}}</ref>不同取景地天气波动显著，达拉斯夏季气温通常在32到46摄氏度<ref name="Warren" />{{rp|19}}<ref name="SyFyAllen" /><ref name="Niderost1">{{cite magazine | last = Niderost | first = Eric | date = 1987-08 | title = Peter Weller Code Name: RoboCop | pages = 45–48 | issue = 121 | magazine = Starlog | publisher = Starlog Group, Inc. | url = https://archive.org/details/starlog_magazine-121/page/n43/mode/2up | access-date = 2022-03-28}}</ref>{{rp|46}}，匹兹堡非常寒冷<ref name="EsquireOral" />。

机器战警服饰是在开拍一段时间后才做好，虽未影响拍摄周期，但威勒穿戴服饰排练一个月的计划落空{{refn|group="注"|见以下文献：<ref name="EsquireOral" /><ref name="IndieWireCast" /><ref name="Warren" />{{rp|19}}<ref name="Niderost1" />{{rp|48}}}}。他看到服饰后非常失望，因为过于笨重，根本没法像练习时那样移动，需长时间适应<ref name="EsquireOral" /><ref name="IndieWireCast" /><ref name="Niderost1" />{{rp|48}}。头盔阻挡视线，戴上手套又很难抓取物体<ref name="Niderost1" />{{rp|48}}<ref name="Niderost" />{{rp|61}}。威勒与范霍文大吵一架后被炒，剧组一度考虑请[[兰斯·亨利克森|兰斯·亨利克森]]代替，但服饰是按威勒的身材制作，其他人鼓励他和导演搞好关系<ref name="IndieWireCast" />。亚基姆协助威勒放慢动作以满足演出需求<ref name="SFX" />。炎热天气对威勒非常不利，他每天流汗达1.4公斤<ref name="IGNHistory" /><ref name="Warren" />{{rp|19}}。压力太大导致他失眠，不得不服用处方药，往往拍摄时药效还没过去<ref>{{cite web | last = Collis | first = Clark | title = RoboCop: Collector's Edition| url = https://ew.com/article/2007/08/20/robocop-collectors-edition/ | website = Entertainment Weekly | date = 2006-08-14 | access-date = 2022-03-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220303042354/https://ew.com/article/2007/08/20/robocop-collectors-edition/ | archive-date = 2022-03-03 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

范霍文经常在开拍前与演员排练<ref name="Bates" />{{rp|17, 20}}<ref name="Niderost" />{{rp|60}}，同时鼓励即兴发挥，希望获得有价值的素材。博迪克部分举动源自史密斯临场发挥，如把口香糖粘在秘书桌子上，把血吐到警局桌台上。据史密斯后来回忆，当时他提出“或许我把血吐在桌上怎么样？……（导演）脸上挂着淡淡的微笑，然后我们就这么拍。”<ref name="EsquireOral" />摄制期间诺麦尔坚持留在一线，有时根据灵感增加剧本情节，例如看到聚会帽子道具后增加新年聚会桥段，还有[[星球大战计划|星球大战计划]]平台故障走火的情节<ref name="EsquireOral" /><ref name="TheDissolveNeumeier" /><ref name="Goldberg" />{{rp|25}}。导演认为诺麦尔在场很有帮助，方便大家讨论调整剧本或取景地，确保桥段达到理想效果<ref name="DallasObserverVerhoeven" />。
[[File:Pittsburgh-steel-company-monessen-works-blast-furnace-no-1-and-no-2-donner-7.jpg|thumb]]

范霍文出了名的不合群，而且经常在片场言语攻击他人。史密斯表示范霍文从不朝演员大喊大叫，只不过太专注工作，没把心思放在交际上。<ref name="EsquireOral" />考克斯与艾伦对导演评价很好<ref name="SyFyAllen" /><ref name="Bates" />{{rp|20}}。威勒拍摄之余同片中扮演反派的演员在一起，如史密斯、怀斯、阮，众人坚持健康的生活习惯，支持威勒为[[紐約馬拉松|紐約馬拉松]]训练<ref name="SFX" />。

剧组在达拉斯及周边许多地点取景。全向消费品内部是在[[文藝復興大廈_(達拉斯)|文艺复兴大厦]]办公室取景，外部采用[[達拉斯市政廳|達拉斯市政廳]]，辅以[[接景|接景]]技术令建筑显得更高{{refn|group="注"|见以下文献：<ref name="DallasHistory" /><ref name="DallasNewsLocations" /><ref name="Niderost" />{{rp|59}}<ref name="DallasFilmCommission">{{cite web | website = Dallas Film Commission | date = 2012 | access-date = 2020-11-08 | url = https://www.dallasfilmcommission.com/robocop-dallas-locations-then-now/ | title = A Look At RoboCop's Dallas Shooting Locations, Shot In 1986 To Current Day 2012. | archive-date = 2020-11-08 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20201108151013/https://www.dallasfilmcommission.com/robocop-dallas-locations-then-now/ | dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref name="Bates" />{{rp|21}}}}。全向消费品的大型升降梯是在[[达拉斯美洲广场|美洲广场]]摄制<ref name="DallasNewsLocations" /><ref name="DallasFilmCommission" />。[[达拉斯高中|克罗泽科技高中]]用于拍摄底特律警察局外景，内景取自[[赫尔曼之子|赫尔曼之子]]大厦，[[达拉斯市政大厦|达拉斯市政大厦]]充当底特律市政厅<ref name="DallasFilmCommission" />。博迪克团伙炸毁店面的镜头在[[迪普埃伦|迪普埃伦]]街区取景，爆炸威力一度超出预期，演员纷纷跑开，史密斯脱掉着火的外套，剧组向参与演员补偿四百美元特技表演费<ref name="EsquireOral" /><ref name="DallasObserverVerhoeven" />。片中爆炸的[[壳牌石油|壳牌石油]]加油站位于[[艺术区_(达拉斯)|艺术区]]<ref name="DallasNewsLocations" /><ref name="DallasFilmCommission" />，不知在拍电影的当地居民报火警<ref name="DallasHistory" />。根据剧本要求，爆炸后的大火形成“地狱”字样，戴维斯同意拍摄但成片未采纳，迈纳非常失望<ref name="EsquireOral" />。

夜总会取景地以前叫斯塔克俱乐部，范霍文向俱乐部成员示范如何跳舞的画面拍入镜头，后在成片采纳<ref name="EsquireOral" /><ref name="VultureTidbits" />。达拉斯取景地还包括[[达拉斯中央快速路|中央快速路]]、[[重逢竞技场|重逢竞技场]]<ref name="DallasFilmCommission" />、[[达拉斯新月|新月]]停车场<ref name="Bates" />{{rp|17}}。片尾机器战警与博迪克团伙的高潮大战是在宾夕法尼亚州[[威斯特摩蘭縣_(賓夕法尼亞州)|威斯特摩兰县]][[莫内森_(宾夕法尼亚州)|莫内森]]、距匹兹堡不远的钢厂摄制{{refn|group="注"|见以下文献：<ref name="ViceNeumeier" /><ref name="DallasObserverVerhoeven" /><ref>{{cite news | last = King | first = Peter B.| url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=57sqAAAAIBAJ&pg=6898%2C7945472 | title = Hollywood Turns To Monessen Steel Plant In Filming 'RoboCop' | work = The Pittsburgh Press | date = 1986-10-29 | page = C6 | access-date = 2022-03-29}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | last1 = Gallagher | first1 = Danny | last2 = Maschino | first2 = Brian | url = https://www.dallasobserver.com/slideshow/robocop-versus-reality-looking-at-dallas-locations-of-the-films-scenes-9647490 | title = ''RoboCop'' Versus Reality: Looking At Dallas Locations Of The Film's Scenes | website = Dallas Observer | date = 2017-07-11 | access-date = 2022-03-29 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211019213014/https://www.dallasobserver.com/slideshow/robocop-versus-reality-looking-at-dallas-locations-of-the-films-scenes-9647490 | archive-date = 2021-10-19 | dead-url = no}}</ref>}}。拍摄工作1986年10月下旬收尾<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|8}}。

=== 后期制作 ===
{{Listen
|filename=Robocop theme - Basil Poledouris.ogg
| title = 《摇滚商店》
|description=巴索·普列多斯谱曲的《机器战警》主题音乐，伦敦室内乐团演出，由管弦乐与合成乐结合而成}}
猎户座影业批准为后期制作和配乐增加60万美元，预算总额升至1370万美元{{refn|group="注"|相当于{{Inflation/year|US}}年{{Format price|{{Inflation|US|13700000|1987}}}}美元。}}{{refn|group="注"|见以下文献：<ref name="UproxxRetro" /><ref name="Goldberg" />{{rp|25}}<ref name="afi" /><ref name="LATimesVerhnMakesGood" />}}。

弗兰克·乌里奥斯特负责本片剪辑<ref name="IndieWire10Things">{{cite web | last = Taylor | first = Drew | title = 10 Reasons Why The Original 'RoboCop' Can't Be Beaten By The Remake | archive-date = 2022-03-10 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20220310174233/https://www.indiewire.com/2014/02/10-reasons-why-the-original-robocop-cant-be-beaten-by-the-remake-89085/ | website = IndieWire | date = 2014-02-13 | access-date = 2022-03-29 | url = https://www.indiewire.com/2014/02/10-reasons-why-the-original-robocop-cant-be-beaten-by-the-remake-89085/ | dead-url = no}}</ref>。墨菲之死、机器战警取下头盔、左腿枪套等镜头是在后期制作阶段补拍<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|23,38}}。根据原本拍摄的素材，机器战警片尾自称墨菲后镜头转向医院，表明刘易斯还活着，最后是机器战警再度上街巡逻。剧组认为观众看到刘易斯在世会产生胜利的满足感，但机器战警独自上街又会削弱这种感觉，决定把两段都剪掉。<ref name="Warren" />{{rp|72}}<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|41}}范霍文希望片中媒体情节突然插入打断剧情，令观众产生焦虑感。[[皮特·蒙德里安|皮特·蒙德里安]]的美术作品以用黑色线条分隔彩色方块，对导演影响很大<ref name="EsquireOral" />。除“TJ雷泽”桥段是诺麦尔导演外，片中媒体报道均由彼得·康恩执导<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|8–9, 24}}。

《机器战警》暴力充斥，很难在[[美國電影協會|美國電影協會]]拿到理想的[[美国电影分级制度|R级]]，即17岁以下观众需成人陪同才能观看。电影初步评为X级，17岁以下观众不能观看。<ref name="EsquireOral" /><ref name="IndieWireCast" /><ref>{{cite web | title = Movies | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1987-05-20-ca-793-story.html | website = Los Angeles Times | date = 1987-05-20 | access-date = 2022-03-29 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210417063938/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1987-05-20-ca-793-story.html | archive-date = 2021-04-17 | dead-url = no}}</ref>媒体宣称电影11次申请评为R级遭拒，范霍文称实际上是八次<ref name="EsquireOral" /><ref name="IndieWireCast" />。美国电影协会对墨菲之死、209执法机器人杀害官员等镜头意见很大<ref name="LATimesVerhnMakesGood" /><ref name="IndieWire10Things" />。后期不得不缩减暴力场面，增加媒体报道内容以便缓解观众情绪。据范霍文回忆，评论家觉得评级修改后的成片风格前后矛盾，质疑是否放映员拿错[[卷筒|卷筒]]。<ref name="IndieWireCast" /><ref name="EsquireOral" />

美国电影协会对埃米尔变异体被博迪克的车肢解同样意见很大，但试映时每到此处观众的笑声总是最大，导演、制片人、制片商都拒绝妥协<ref name="UproxxRetro" /><ref name="Warren" />{{rp|20}}。范霍文有意令暴力桥段显得滑稽而且脱离现实，觉得修剪后镜头实际上更血腥<ref name="EsquireOral" /><ref name="IndieWireCast" />。他还记得年幼的孩子在看X级版时大笑，R级版上映时观众发笑的镜头反而减少<ref name="EsquireOral" /><ref name="LATimesVerhnMakesGood" />。在他看来，人们“喜欢看暴力和可怕的事物”<ref name="LATimesVerhnMakesGood" />。完整版《机器战警》长103分钟<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.bbfc.co.uk/release/robocop-q29sbgvjdglvbjpwwc0yotuyndc | title = RoboCop | publisher = [[英國電影分級委員會|British Board of Film Classification]] | access-date = 2022-03-29 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20220310125701/https://www.bbfc.co.uk/release/robocop-q29sbgvjdglvbjpwwc0yotuyndc | archive-date = 2022-03-10 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

曾与范霍文在《冷血奇兵》合作的巴索·普列多斯为本片[[電影配樂|谱曲]]<ref name="DOGWhereareThey" />，配乐乃管弦乐与合成乐结合而成，反映主角的半机器人本质。乐曲由[[伦敦室内乐团|伦敦室内乐团]]演奏。<ref>{{cite web | title = RoboCop | url = https://www.filmtracks.com/titles/robocop.html | website = Filmtracks.com | date = 2004-01-30 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20220309180436/https://www.filmtracks.com/titles/robocop.html | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2022-03-09 | access-date = 2022-03-29}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = The 80 Greatest Movies Of The '80s | url = https://sinfoniaoflondon.com/about/ | website = Sinfonia of London | access-date = 2022-03-29 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20220302051908/https://sinfoniaoflondon.com/about/ | archive-date = 2022-03-02 | dead-url = no}}</ref>

== 特效与设计 ==

=== 特效 ===
[[File:RoboCop_1987_Melting_Man.jpg|thumb]]

[[罗伯·博汀|罗伯·博汀]]带队《机器战警》特效工作组，主要成员包括[[菲尔·蒂贝特|菲尔·蒂贝特]]、斯蒂凡·杜普里斯、巴特·米克森、克雷格·海耶斯等{{refn|group="注"|见以下文献：<ref name="UproxxRetro" /><ref name="Niderost" />{{rp|61}}<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|12, 15}}<ref name="Niderost1" />{{rp|46, 48}}}}。

本片特效极尽暴力，导演认为这能让镜头显得好笑<ref name="EsquireOral" /><ref name="IndieWireCast" />。他觉得墨菲之死残忍程度可比[[耶穌被釘十字架|耶穌被釘十字架]]，肯定能马上激起观众同情<ref name="EsquireOral" /><ref name="IndieWire10Things" /><ref name="Warren" />{{rp|20}}。这场戏在加利福尼亚州[[長灘_(加利福尼亞州)|长滩]]的废弃装配厂拍摄，镜头对准抬升起来的操作台，方便工作人员在下面控制效果<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|23}}。为真实呈现子弹在墨菲身上打出连串孔洞，剧组利用[[海藻酸|藻酸盐]]制作假肢，里面的[[管子_(流體輸送)|管子]]泵入人造血和压缩空气。人造左臂用[[尼龙搭扣|尼龙搭扣]]附在威勒肩膀，由三名操作员控制，手臂能以可控手法炸开，方便重新组装后再拍。<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|23}}人造右臂连以[[单丝钓线|单丝钓线]]，方便猛然扯离威勒的躯干<ref name="ViceNeumeier" /><ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|23}}。剧组根据威勒上半身制作细节非常清晰的复制品，用于拍摄博迪克开枪命中墨菲头部的镜头<ref name="Warren" />{{rp|20}}<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|23}}<ref name="Niderost3">{{cite magazine | last = Niderost | first = Eric | date = 1987-08 | title = Robocop Rob | pages = 20–23 | issue = 66 | magazine = Fangoria | publisher = Fangoria Publishing, LLC | location = [[亚特兰大|Atlanta, Georgia]] | url = https://issuu.com/fangoriafans/docs/fangoria__066__the_lost_boys_ | access-date = 2022-03-29}}</ref>。人物脸部是用泡沫[[乳胶|乳胶]]制模，烘烤后就像肉一样很有弹力；头骨采用玻璃纤维制成，内含血袋和炸药。头部由四名木偶师控制，上面的汗和血清晰可见。假体附加风扇产生震动，仿佛怕得发抖。头骨内含引爆电荷通过电线与史密斯所持枪支的扳机相连，确保效果同步。<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|23–24}}

埃米尔变异并融化的画面灵感源自1977年科幻片《[[不可思议的融化人|不可思议的融化人]]》<ref name="EmilGamesRadar">{{cite web | title = 50 Greatest Movie Make-Up Effects (Page 3) | date = 2013-01-21 | access-date = 2022-03-29 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.gamesradar.com/50-greatest-movie-make-up-effects/3/ | website = [[GamesRadar+|GamesRadar+]] | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20220303042354/https://www.gamesradar.com/50-greatest-movie-make-up-effects/3/ | archive-date = 2022-03-03}}</ref>，博汀设计并制作埃米尔的假体，用泡沫乳胶头饰和配套手套营造人物皮肤融化的效果，“仿佛棉花糖酱从他骨头上剥落”<ref name="EmilGamesRadar" /><ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|39}}，外面套上第二套假体营造进一步融化效果。杜普里斯为每套假体画上不同效果，凸显人物融化过程，再把假体装到铰接假人上，拍摄博迪克的车撞上埃米尔桥段。假人头部事先松脱以便撞飞，滚到汽车发动机盖上纯属偶然。埃米尔的躯体最后全部液化流下挡风玻璃，液体是生鸡肉、汤、肉汁混合而成。<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|39}}高潮大战时当头砸倒机器战警的钢梁其实是漆木，用于拍摄的假人就是埃米尔撞车那个<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|39}}。范霍文本想由机器战警从眼睛捅死博迪克，但因担心无法过审放弃<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|40}}。

片尾迪克·琼斯摔死的镜头由罗科·焦弗雷采用静止木偶动画制作。准备时间有限，采用高质量的铰接式人偶根本来不及，只能用铝质骨架配合泡沫橡胶制作。人偶摔落的街道采用马克·沙利文画作接景摄制。<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|40}}<ref name="Bates" />{{rp|23}}209执法机器人杀害凯文·佩奇所饰高管的镜头耗时三天，佩奇身上带着两百个血袋，但范霍文对效果不满意，几个月后请回佩奇在制片厂搭建的董事会大厅重拍。除两百多个血袋外，佩奇身上还有装满[[金絲瓜|金絲瓜]]和假血的塑料袋。他感觉每次血袋引爆都像挨打，拍摄过程痛得要命。<ref name="THRPage" />摄制毒品仓库动作戏时，博迪克的替身演员摔向真玻璃，玻璃内含导爆索，在人物接触前几微秒爆破<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|32}}。为营造子弹打中机器战警时弹开的效果，剧组用气枪发射装有[[木糠|木糠]]的明胶胶囊<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|31–32}}。

=== 机器战警 ===
博汀负责设计机器战警服饰<ref name="EsquireOral" /><ref name="UproxxRetro" /><ref name="Niderost3" />。他研究《星球大战》角色[[C-3PO|C-3PO]]，僵硬的服装令演员难以动作<ref name="Niderost3" />。《[[大都會_(1927年電影)|大都会]]》与《[[地球停转之日|地球停转之日]]》的机器人<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|7}}<ref name="IndieWire10Things" />，乃至漫画超级英雄设计都对他影响很大。范霍文希望人物看起来更像机器，提出的修改意见促使博汀创作近50种设计<ref name="Bates1">{{cite magazine | last = Bates | first = Dan | date = 1987-10 | title = The Making of RoboCop | page = 19 | issue = 1 | volume = 18 | magazine = Cinefantastique | publisher = Fourth Castle Micromedia | location = Forest Park, Illinois | url = https://archive.org/details/cinefantastique_1970-2002/Cinefantastique%20Vol%2018%20No%201%20%28Dec%201987%29/page/n17/mode/2up | access-date = 2022-03-30}}</ref><ref name="Niderost3" />，最后采纳的圆润美感设计灵感源自日本插画家[[空山基|空山基]]<ref>{{Cite episode | title = RoboCop | series = The Movies That Made Us | type = Television production | network = [[Netflix|Netflix]] | last = Volk-Weiss | first = Brian | season = 3 | number = 4 | air-date = 2021-10-12 | at = 28:00}}</ref>。范霍文自承看过[[日本漫画|日本科幻漫画]]后产生不切实际的期望并浪费太多时间，导致机器战警服饰迟迟不能完工<ref name="EsquireOral" />。

机器战警服饰多方面要求前所未有，设计与制作均超时超支<ref name="DallasObserverVerhoeven" /><ref name="Niderost3" /><ref name="Warren" />{{rp|19}}。服饰制作耗时半年，主要采用柔韧的泡沫乳胶、半刚硬或全刚硬[[聚氨酯|聚氨酯]]，头盔采用玻璃纤维<ref name="Bates1" /><ref name="Niderost3" /><ref name="Warren" />{{rp|19}}。活动部分以铝和滚珠轴承连接，服饰整体以内部钩具支撑，满足动作场面连串活动需要<ref name="Niderost3" />。剧组共制作七套机器战警服饰，包含可防火或承受损伤的版本<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|27}}。服饰重量记载不一但最轻也有11公斤，最重36公斤{{refn|group="注"|见以下文献：<ref name="DOGDiminishing">{{cite web | last = Cecchini | first = Mike | url = https://www.denofgeek.com/movies/robocop-the-franchise-of-diminishing-returns/ | title = RoboCop: The Franchise Of Diminishing Returns | website = Den of Geek | date = 2019-02-12 | access-date = 2022-03-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220303042354/https://www.denofgeek.com/movies/robocop-the-franchise-of-diminishing-returns/ | archive-date = 2022-03-03 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="Bates" />{{rp|18}}<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|26}}<ref name="Warren" />{{rp|19}}}}。机器战警配备的[[貝瑞塔93R手槍|貝瑞塔93R手槍]]枪管加长，枪把加大，经改装用于发射[[空包彈|空包彈]]，侧边的通风口令枪每打出三枚子弹就会朝多方向闪光一次<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|19, 27}}。

=== 209型机器人 ===
[[File:You_have_20_seconds_to_comply._(2423554).jpg|thumb]]

蒂贝特绘制初步草图，请戴维斯设计全尺寸模型，保拉·卢切斯协助制作，为209型机器人开发争取预算<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|12, 15}}。范霍文希望机器人一看就显得不好惹，感觉戴维斯的初步设计缺乏“杀手”感。戴维斯的设计受[[虎鯨|虎鯨]]和[[美国空军|美国空军]][[A-7海盜二式攻擊機|A-7海盜二式攻擊機]]影响，他认为现代美国美学和企业设计政策重视外观甚于功能，常有过度或不切实际的零件。为避免机器人显出同情心，他没有设计眼睛。<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|15}}全尺寸铰接玻璃纤维模型耗资2.5万美元，重140到230公斤，高2.1米，制造耗时四个月<ref name="Bates2">{{cite magazine | last = Bates | first = Dan | date = 1987-12 | title = The Making of ED-209 | page = 25 | issue = 1 | volume = 18 |magazine = Cinefantastique | publisher = Fourth Castle Micromedia | location = Forest Park, Illinois | url = https://archive.org/details/cinefantastique_1970-2002/Cinefantastique%20Vol%2018%20No%201%20%28Dec%201987%29/page/n23/mode/2up | access-date = 2022-03-30}}</ref><ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|15–16}}<ref name="Bates" />{{rp|24}}。戴维斯等人每周工作100小时并持续数周，他预计镜头不会拍到机器人的脚，所以做得很粗糙<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|16}}。模型后用来巡回宣传<ref name="Bates2" /><ref name="Bates" />{{rp|24}}<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|16, 40}}。

戴维斯又花四个月制作两台高30厘米的微缩模型，用于制作[[定格动画|定格动画]]。两台模型提升动画制作和拍摄效率，节省55组镜头所需三个月时间。<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|16, 19}}209型机器人动画由蒂贝特负责，兰德尔·杜特拉与哈里·沃尔顿协助<ref name="UproxxRetro" /><ref name="Bates2" /><ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|19–20}}。蒂贝特有意令机器人动作显得生硬、不自然，一看就不像生命体，仿佛总是在摔倒前一刻才达到平衡<ref name="Bates2" />。机器人发出豹子般的咆哮，戴维森临时为语音部分配音，最后在成片保留<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|20}}。

=== 其他效果和设计 ===
《机器战警》所含七段接景镜头的画作基本由焦弗雷绘制，都画在绝缘纤维板上。他在现场监督拍摄，在拍摄接景画面时根据需要遮挡摄像机镜头。据焦弗雷回忆，为取得美洲广场的理想镜头，他一度爬出五楼窗口。<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|11}}机器战警商标的磨光钢板效果采用特殊摄影技术制作，彼得·库兰根据猎户座影业的黑白商标素描设计。库兰制作放大的接景版商标并采用[[背光照明|背光照明]]。为取得反光细节，他还制有背面是铝板的第二版。<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|8}}剧组用[[乙酸盐|乙酸盐]]在摄制素材胶片上画出数以百计的线条，呈现机器战警与人类不同的视野。线条起初不是太粗就是太细，反复尝试才达成理想效果。<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|24}}库兰估计[[红外摄影|热成像摄像]]价格高昂，在演员的紧身衣上画出热成像色彩，再用[[偏振片|偏振片]]镜头拍摄<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|28}}。美术总监盖尔·西蒙监督制作全向消费品会议室的德尔塔城模型<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|12}}。

片中警车是漆成黑色的1986年版[[福特金牛座_(第一代)|福特金牛座]]<ref name="LAtimesDesign" />，这款符合空气动力学的最新车型颇具未来美感，电影拍摄时刚刚投产。剧组原计划在车内设计复杂设施，可查询人脸照片、指纹等信息，但因过于繁杂放弃。<ref name="UproxxRetro" /><ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|8}}博迪克等人驾驶的6000 SUX其实是[[奥兹莫比尔超级短剑|奥兹莫比尔超级短剑]]，由[[吉恩·温菲尔德|吉恩·温菲尔德]]根据[[奇普·富斯|奇普·富斯]]的设计改装而成。剧组制作两台功能正常车型，还有一台无功能车用于拍摄爆炸桥段。<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|35–36}}6000 SUX电视广告里的恐龙是橡皮泥捏成，唐·沃勒制作动画，[[齊奧多兄弟|史蒂夫·奇奥多]][[舞台调度|调度]]<ref name="Sammon" />{{rp|35–36}}。

