=== 文化影响 ===
《机器战警》为科幻片开创新类型<ref name="IndieWire10Things" />。与同期许多电影主角不同，机器战警不像机器般清心寡欲、所向披靡，而是类似人类的机器人，明显受昔日人格影响<ref name="IndieWire10Things" />。底特律破产并被评为美国最危险的地方后，诺麦尔在2013年接受采访谈论本片远见。在他看来，美国人“现在就生活在《机器战警》中的世界……大企业将如何照顾我们……又会如何罔顾我们”。<ref name="GuericaMag" /><ref>{{cite web | first = Oliver | last = Joy | title = ''RoboCop'' Creator: Detroit Shows The Film's Fictional Future Is Upon Us | url = https://edition.cnn.com/2013/07/25/business/robocop-neumeier-detroit-bankruptcy/index.html# | website = [[底特律自由新聞|Detroit Free Press]] | date = 2013-07-25 | access-date = 2022-04-01 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20220303165039/https://edition.cnn.com/2013/07/25/business/robocop-neumeier-detroit-bankruptcy/index.html | archive-date = 2022-03-03 | dead-url = no}}</ref>范霍文声称《机器战警》领先时代，这是数字效果做不到的<ref name="ActionEW">{{cite web | archive-date = 2009-02-21 | dead-url = yes | url = http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20041669_20041686_20042607_12,00.html | title = The 25 Greatest Action Films Ever! | website = Entertainment Weekly | access-date = 2009-02-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090221132614/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20041669_20041686_20042607_12,00.html}}</ref>。威勒自认拍摄本片非常辛苦，最主要的原因便是机器战警服饰<ref>{{cite web | first = Roger | last = Ebert | url = https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/robocop-3-1993 | title = RoboCop 3 | website = RogerEbert.com | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211030173641/https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/robocop-3-1993 | date = 1993-11-05 | access-date = 2022-04-01 | archive-date = 2021-10-30 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。范霍文同样感觉拍摄《机器战警》非常痛苦，主因包括特效难以制作和遇到的种种困境<ref name="Niderost2" />。弗尔对此感观相反，自认这是一辈子最开心的暑期<ref name="AVClubFerrer" />。

本片影响不局限于北美，诺麦尔记得在[[罗马斗兽场|罗马斗兽场]]附近看到未经许可的机器战警玩偶销售<ref name="TheDissolveNeumeier" />。他指出，许多机器人实验室项目名称在本片影响下以“{{lang|en|Robo}}”开头，参与《机器战警》更是美国空军请他当顾问提供未来构想的直接原因<ref name="ViceNeumeier" />。影片上映后，范霍文接连执导热卖科幻片《[[全面回忆|全面回忆]]》和[[情色驚悚片|情色驚悚片]]《[[第六感追緝令|第六感追緝令]]》，其中前者也有罗尼·考克斯参演<ref name="DOGWhereareThey" /><ref name="CBRCast" />。1997年他与诺麦尔再度合作的科幻片《[[星河戰隊_(電影)|星河战队]]》问世<ref name="DOGWhereareThey" />。2020年《[[衛報|衛報]]》刊登斯科特·托比亚斯的文章，认为《机器战警》开创范霍文威权统治非正式科幻动作片三部曲，后两部分别是《全面回忆》和《星河战队》<ref>{{cite web | first = Scott | last = Tobias | title = Total Recall at 30: A Thrilling Reminder Of Paul Verhoeven At His Best | url = https://www.theguardian.com/film/2020/jun/01/total-recall-paul-verhoeven-at-his-best | website = The Guardian | date =  2020-06-01 | archive-date = 2022-03-24 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2022-04-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220324203427/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2020/jun/01/total-recall-paul-verhoeven-at-his-best}}</ref>。以往戏路基本局限在好好先生的考克斯认为本片和《比佛利山超级警探》系列令他改头换面，大幅推动他的电影生涯，成为80年代极具代表的反派演员<ref name="LATimesRonnyCox" /><ref name="AVClubCox" /><ref>{{cite web | last = Gilchrist | first = Todd | title = Why ''RoboCop'', 'Total Recall' Villain Ronny Cox Hates Remakes: 'Those Films Hold Up Pretty Damn Well' | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/general-news/robocop-total-recall-ronny-cox-remakes-deliverance-343132/ | website = The Hollywood Reporter | date = 2012-06-28 | access-date = 2022-04-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210623194001/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/general-news/robocop-total-recall-ronny-cox-remakes-deliverance-343132/ | archive-date = 2021-06-23 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

