== 续作与改编 ==
猎户座影业早在1987年11月就为续集开发亮绿灯，要求以[[電影分級制度|PG级]]为目标，儿童无需成人陪同就能观看<ref>{{cite web | title = First Off . . . | archive-date = 2021-04-17 | dead-url = no | date = 1987-08-07 | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1987-08-07-ca-1062-story.html | website = Los Angeles Times | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210417064018/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1987-08-07-ca-1062-story.html | access-date = 2022-04-02}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | last = Klady | first = Leonard | title = Sequels: A Follow-Up | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1987-11-01-ca-17949-story.html | website = Los Angeles Times | date = 1987-11-01 | access-date = 2022-04-02 | archive-date = 2022-03-02 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220302203041/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1987-11-01-ca-17949-story.html}}</ref><ref name="Goldberg" />{{rp|25, 72}}，计划与1988年[[漫威制片|漫威制片]]推出的12集动画片《机器战警》同步发行<ref name="IGNHistory" /><ref name="IndieWire10Things" />。诺麦尔与迈纳开始编剧，但因[[1988年美国编剧协会大罢工|1988年美国编剧协会大罢工]]期间拒绝工作被炒，取而代之的[[弗兰克·米勒|弗兰克·米勒]]所创第二稿剧本拍成《机器战警2》，第一稿拍成《机器战警3》<ref name="TheDissolveNeumeier" /><ref name="Goldberg" />{{rp|72}}。威勒在[[爾文·克許納|爾文·克許納]]导演的《机器战警2》再度出演主人翁<ref>{{cite web | first = Andrew | last = Renyolds | title = Looking back At RoboCop 2 | url = https://www.denofgeek.com/movies/looking-back-at-robocop-2/ | website = Den of Geek | date = 2013-05-21 | access-date = 2022-04-02 | archive-date = 2022-03-10 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220310063648/https://www.denofgeek.com/movies/looking-back-at-robocop-2/}}</ref>，影片反响不佳，估计制片商最后亏本<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/robocop_2 | title = RoboCop 2 | archive-date = 2022-03-09 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2022-04-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220309195619/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/robocop_2}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Geraldine | last = Fabrikant | title = The Media Business; Orion Sees Its Financial Star Fade | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1990/08/13/business/the-media-business-orion-sees-its-financial-star-fade.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1990-08-13 | access-date = 2022-04-02 | page = D6 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220303004848/https://www.nytimes.com/1990/08/13/business/the-media-business-orion-sees-its-financial-star-fade.html | archive-date = 2022-03-03 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

《机器战警3》由[[弗莱德·戴克尔|弗莱德·戴克尔]]导演，主要面向能推动商品销售的青少年观众。[[羅伯特·約翰·伯克|羅伯特·約翰·伯克]]取代威勒扮演机器战警，艾伦第三次也是最后一次扮演刘易斯。<ref name="IGNHistory" /><ref name="SyFyAllen" /><ref name="IndieWire10Things" />影片口碑票房双仆街<ref>{{cite web | first = Ryan | last = Lambie | title = 10 Remarkable Things About RoboCop 3 | website = Den of Geek | access-date = 2022-04-02 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.denofgeek.com/movies/10-remarkable-things-about-robocop-3/ | date = 2012-09-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220321102519/https://www.denofgeek.com/movies/10-remarkable-things-about-robocop-3/ | archive-date = 2022-03-21}}</ref>。1994年[[机器战警_(1994年电视剧)|电影同名真人电视剧]]面世，但同样评价不佳，22集后停播。剧中主人翁由理查德·伊顿扮演，诺麦尔和迈纳参与制作并沿用创作《机器战警2》的构想。<ref name="IGNHistory" /><ref name="IndieWire10Things" /><ref name="DOGDiminishing" />1998年动画片《[[机械战警：阿尔法突击队|机械战警：阿尔法突击队]]》问世<ref name="IGNHistory" /><ref name="IndieWire10Things" />。[[佩奇·弗莱彻|佩奇·弗莱彻]]在2001年四集真人电视剧《[[机械战警：终极毁灭|机械战警：终极毁灭]]》扮演主人翁，剧情发生在原版《机器战警》十年后，不考虑续作剧情<ref name="IGNHistory" /><ref name="IndieWire10Things" />。在金融泥潭挣扎多年后，猎户座影业及手中《机器战警》版权均在20世纪末由米高梅收购<ref name="IGNHistory" /><ref name="THRReturns">{{cite web | first =  Borys | last = Kit | title = 'Robocop Returns' Lands 'Little Monsters' Director Abe Forsythe (Exclusive) | archive-date = 2022-01-15 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/robocop-returns-lands-little-monsters-director-abe-forsythe-1256699/ | website = The Hollywood Reporter | date = 2019-11-20 | access-date = 2022-04-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220115163511/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/robocop-returns-lands-little-monsters-director-abe-forsythe-1256699/}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = MGM To Get Orion Assets | url = https://www.upi.com/Archives/1997/07/10/MGM-to-get-Orion-assets/6732868507200/ | website = [[合众国际社|United Press International]] | date = 1997-07-10 | access-date = 2022-04-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220310125702/https://www.upi.com/Archives/1997/07/10/MGM-to-get-Orion-assets/6732868507200/ | archive-date = 2022-03-10 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

[[何塞·帕蒂尔哈|何塞·帕蒂尔哈]]执导的[[机械战警_(2014年电影)|2014年同名电影]]是1987年原版[[重启_(虚构)|重启]]之作，[[喬爾·金納曼|喬爾·金納曼]]饰演机器战警，影片评价不一但票房热卖<ref name="TheDissolveNeumeier" /><ref name="DeadlineBlomkamp" /><ref>{{cite web | first = Mark | last = Birrell | title = 5 Reasons Why RoboCop 2014 Isn't As Bad As People Say It Is (& 5 Reasons It Is) | url = https://screenrant.com/reasons-robocop-2014-remake-joel-kinnman-bad-good-movie-underrated/ | website = Screen Rant | date = 2020-06-03 | access-date = 2022-04-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220309180436/https://screenrant.com/reasons-robocop-2014-remake-joel-kinnman-bad-good-movie-underrated/ | archive-date = 2022-03-09 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。范霍文觉得应该在他去世后才有“重启”作品问世，艾伦认为已成为影史标志的电影不该重拍<ref name="SyFyAllen" />。进入开发阶段的《机器战警归来》计划忽略所有续作，直接延续1987年原作剧情。影片计划由[[亚伯·福赛斯|亚伯·福赛斯]]导演，福赛斯还在改写诺麦尔、迈纳、贾斯汀·罗德斯创作的剧本。<ref name="THRReturns" /><ref>{{cite web | first = Drew | last = Turney | title = Screenwriter Ed Neumeier On Disguising 'Tougher Issues' Behind Genre And RoboCop Returns' Future | url = https://www.syfy.com/syfy-wire/robocop-returns-ed-neumeier-starship-troopers | website = Syfy | date = 2020-09-01 | access-date = 2022-04-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220222212912/https://www.syfy.com/syfy-wire/robocop-returns-ed-neumeier-starship-troopers | archive-date = 2022-02-22 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Louis | last = Chilton | title = New RoboCop Movie Will Be A Direct Sequel To The Original | url = https://www.radiotimes.com/tv/sci-fi/robocop-returns-reboot-sequel/ | website = [[广播时报|Radio Times]] | date = 2019-11-21 | access-date = 2022-04-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220316201204/https://www.radiotimes.com/tv/sci-fi/robocop-returns-reboot-sequel/ | archive-date = 2022-03-16 | dead-url = no}}</ref>诺麦尔2020年接受采访时透露，《机器战警》前传电视剧尚在开发，重点介绍迪克·琼斯青年时代和全向消费品公司崛起<ref>{{cite web | title = Exclusive : MGM working on RoboCop series focusing on young Dick Jones | url = https://moviehole.net/exclusive-mgm-working-on-robocop-series-focusing-on-young-dick-jones/ | work = MovieHole | last = Turney | first = Drew | date = 2020-09-09 | access-date = 2022-04-02 | archive-date = 2021-04-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210418181121/https://moviehole.net/exclusive-mgm-working-on-robocop-series-focusing-on-young-dick-jones/ | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

